{"name":"Loaded Naan Pizzas","slug":"loaded-naan-pizzas","description":"","ingredients":[{"name":"fresh cauliflower florets","quantity":"3 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lentils","quantity":"1 can (19 oz/540 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"light mayonnaise","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Roasted Garlic Aioli Mix","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lemon juice","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tsp","additionalInstruction":"optional"},{"name":"whole wheat naans","quantity":"4 small","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Mango Curry Dip Mix","quantity":"2 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tbsp","additionalInstruction":"divided"},{"name":"oil","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Preheat oven to 400° F</li>\n  <li>Chop cauliflower into bite sized pieces. Combine with 2 tbsp dip mix and oil. Place in a single layer on a <a data-item-id=\"423693c7-df9f-4960-8715-f08b2d79dead\" href=\"/en-us/product/sheet-pan\">Sheet Pan</a> lined with a <a data-item-id=\"457bbcd8-77a0-4a70-96c9-951018a3fc9c\" href=\"/en-us/product/sheet-pan-liner\">Sheet Pan Liner</a>. Roast until tender, 15–17 min.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, combine mayonnaise, aioli mix, and lemon juice in a small bowl. Set aside.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Wrap naan in foil; warm in oven for last 7–10 min of roasting.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, drain and rinse lentils. Combine with remaining <sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>2</sub> tbsp dip mix in<a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"/en-us/product/multipurpose-steamer\"> Multipurpose Steamer</a>. Cover; microwave on high until warm, 2–3 min.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>To serve, spread aioli on warmed naan; top with lentils, cauliflower, and toppings, if desired.&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"steamers","name":"Steamers"},{"slug":"dairy_free","name":"Dairy-free"},{"slug":"gfrr_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"sheet_pan_3e5bebd","name":"Sheet Pan"},{"slug":"vegetarian","name":"Vegetarian"},{"slug":"gfrr_dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"onion_free","name":"Onion-free"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":520,"fat":19,"saturatedFat":3,"transFat":0,"cholesterol":10,"sodium":640,"carbohydrate":74,"fiber":12,"sugars":7,"protein":20},"tips":"<p>Warm up your naan bread in your <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"/en-us/product/multipurpose-steamer\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>—Simply microwave, covered, on high for 30 sec.&nbsp;</p>","perfectlyBalanceYourPlate":"<p>Serve with 1 cup mixed veggies.&nbsp;</p>"}